perations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2685108225","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685108225","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTEwODIyNQ==","status":"current","title":"Iniciativas","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":274391100},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685108225/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685108225/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685108225/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685108225/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685108225","tinyui":"/x/AYALo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685108225","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685108225/Iniciativas","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685108225"}},{"id":"2760147005","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2760147005","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjc2MDE0NzAwNQ==","status":"current","title":"Iniciativas en Curso","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":258},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"3022520346","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3022520346","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzAyMjUyMDM0Ng==","status":"current","title":"BAU","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":868},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3022520346","tinyui":"/x/GgAot","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3022520346","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3022520346/BAU","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3022520346"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>La tarea consiste en agregar un nuevo requerimiento para procesar un campo adicional de forma opcional llamado <code>track2</code> en la confirmaci&oacute;n de un c&oacute;digo QR de HST. El <code>track2</code> estar&aacute; anidado dentro del campo <code>encToken</code>, que ya est&aacute; siendo recibido encriptado en el campo <code>encryptedData</code> del JSON.</p><p /><h3>Desglose de la tarea:</h3><ol start=\"1\"><li><p><strong>Datos actuales recibidos</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>El campo <code>encToken</code> ya contiene la siguiente informaci&oacute;n:</p><ul><li><p><code>algorithm</code>: Algoritmo de encriptaci&oacute;n usado, en este caso <code>aes-gcm256</code>.</p></li><li><p><code>iv</code>: Vector de inicializaci&oacute;n para la encriptaci&oacute;n.</p></li><li><p><code>encryptedData</code>: Datos encriptados que contienen la informaci&oacute;n, incluyendo ahora el nuevo campo <code>track2</code>.</p></li><li><p><code>MACLength</code>: Longitud del c&oacute;digo de autenticaci&oacute;n de mensaje (MAC).</p></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Nuevo campo</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>El nuevo campo opcional <code>track2</code> se incluir&aacute; en los datos encriptados que ya se reciben bajo el campo <code>encryptedData</code>.</p></li><li><p>El formato del contenido encriptado incluir&aacute;:</p><ul><li><p><code>token</code>: Un identificador del token.</p></li><li><p><code>expirationMonth</code> y <code>expirationYear</code>: Mes y a&ntilde;o de expiraci&oacute;n del token.</p></li><li><p><code>track2</code>: Informaci&oacute;n adicional opcional.</p></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>JSON actualizado</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>La estructura que ahora contendr&aacute; el nuevo campo <code>track2</code> ser&aacute; similar al siguiente ejemplo: <br /></p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"7a024bbf-d3c5-414f-942a-539b5e4b4bd8\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"language\">json</ac:parameter><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[{\n  \"encToken\": {\n    \"algorithm\": \"aes-gcm256\",\n    \"iv\": \"00112233445566778899aabbccddeeff\",\n    \"encryptedData\": \"XWyKOTY51KBJMVsWxHc=\",\n    \"MACLength\": \"12\"\n  }\n}]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>Dentro del campo encriptado <code>encryptedData</code>, el valor incluir&aacute; algo como:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"9403e85e-8d98-44c2-8c67-9b7ec55560a7\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[{\n  \"token\": \"4321000000001234\",\n  \"expirationMonth\": \"12\",\n  \"expirationYear\": \"2024\",\n  \"track2\": \"HBAHSGDJAJHD\"\n}]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Branch</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Debes partir de la rama <code>feature/fix-visa-qr</code>, ya que incluye algunas mejoras relacionadas que pueden ser &uacute;tiles para esta tarea.</p></li></ul></li></ol><h3>Pasos a seguir:</h3><ol start=\"1\"><li><p><strong>Decodificar el campo </strong><code>encryptedData</code> para verificar si el campo <code>track2</code> est&aacute; presente.</p></li><li><p><strong>Modificar la l&oacute;gica</strong> que maneja el campo <code>encToken</code> para gestionar el nuevo campo <code>track2</code> de forma opcional. Es decir, si <code>track2</code> est&aacute; presente, procesarlo, y si no, continuar normalmente.</p></li><li><p><strong>Actualizar la documentaci&oacute;n</strong> y pruebas unitarias para incluir el manejo de este nuevo campo en el flujo de confirmaci&oacute;n del QR.</p></li></ol><p>Este ajuste permitir&aacute; que, en el futuro, el campo <code>track2</code> pueda ser procesado cuando sea enviado dentro del token encriptado.</p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3348365333"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":2810},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3348365333/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3348365333/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3348365333/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3348365333/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3348365333","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3348365333/QBK-107+-+Agregar+el+dato+del+track2+en+la+confirmaci+n+de+qr+de+hst","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3348365333","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3348365333","tinyui":"/x/FQCUxw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}